item.title: ICPC Swag — Team Bruteforce
item.description: Our ICPC team Bruteforce — Rishik Varma, Jatin Singh and me were able to quality for the ACM ICPC Amritapuri Regionals and secure a rank of 264 (College rank 2) and the ACM ICPC Gwalior-Pune regionals with a rank of 200(College rank 2) . I blogged about the experience here on Medium.
